summary.description:

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in light levels (up 7094 lux) and cloud levels (up 550 m).

The past week and month had observable variation in light levels (up 7363 lux), cloud levels (up 997 m), feels like temperature (up 3.7°C), and outside temperature (up 2.8°C) when compared to today.
